{"tid":598410,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"每次炒車就話係假日司機","createTime":"2018-03-19T13:00:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-26T05:07:16.000Z","uid":48605,"like":85,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"ca600b35cf8e8c553d2d430ea8c080397edf5636","tid":598410,"uid":48605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T13:00:33.000Z","msg":"屌你老母啦！<br />\n不知幾多職業司機，日日揸車既以為自己車神<br />\n轉彎唔打燈，亂cut線<br />\n好心啲柒頭，分分鐘車牌都冇既，唔好懶醒次次都話係假日司機，P牌仔<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n利申: 假日司機<br />\n但因為自己小揸，所以每次都好小心，跟足規矩，唔超車，唔超速，轉彎一定打燈"},{"pid":"f24a786cf84c50f5dbed712e5732d6bac23aceaa","tid":598410,"uid":42314,"like":58,"dislike":1,"score":57,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T13:02:58.000Z","msg":"以前我P牌個陣跟足路牌限速行最左線都比人呠 夜晚揸又試過比人閃大燈玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港D司機既質素真係得啖笑"},{"pid":"7c1a3bb4478b79b57344c058a6f18f2d8a2e1767","tid":598410,"uid":75448,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T13:03:19.000Z","msg":"好多時意外就係輸行車經驗，唔到你話唔係假日司機的問題。"},{"pid":"031546d8a9e22a8f65ad80baeca3c6625421cd5a","tid":598410,"uid":48605,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"7c1a3bb4478b79b57344c058a6f18f2d8a2e1767","tid":598410,"uid":75448,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T13:03:19.000Z","msg":"好多時意外就係輸行車經驗，唔到你話唔係假日司機的問題。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T13:06:59.000Z","msg":"所以唔明啲人成日炒車就話係假日司機<br />\n其實最近啲意外，有幾多單係P牌仔？<br />\n根本小巴的士最多，其實係心態問題，啲人以為熟能生巧就唔會炒咁"},{"pid":"1ad8d923fc5b11e7e09fb6a2ce260a5d650aca74","tid":598410,"uid":48605,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"f24a786cf84c50f5dbed712e5732d6bac23aceaa","tid":598410,"uid":42314,"like":58,"dislike":1,"score":57,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T13:02:58.000Z","msg":"以前我P牌個陣跟足路牌限速行最左線都比人呠 夜晚揸又試過比人閃大燈玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/face